text.tspan: We’re a team of people just like you. People who struggled to find the right fit for their talent, and wondered if they were ever going to feel fulfilled. People who have felt trapped in their job and were unable to find one that they love.
People who needed guidance but didn’t know where to find it.

We started Lantern because it’s something we needed but didn’t have. Trying to find the right career is hard enough, and going it alone only makes it worse. Our team of entrepreneurs, psychologists, and industry experts are here to make sure you have

the support you need to find the right path for you.We’re a team of people just like you.
